description: The Quintessential typeface is a calligraphic lettering style based on the Italic Hand. As speed became more essential in writing hands, styles became less formal and more relaxed. Classic, clean, and casual, Quintessential fits a lot of design uses - hence its name. To contribute to the project contact Brian J. Bonislawsky.
